# get_irida_analysis_output_files
# download all output files from a completed analysis
# PROJECT_ID is used only for tab completion, not passed to the API
# ANALYSIS_ID is the actual argument used in the curl call
#
# example: get_irida_analysis_output_files [TAB for project id] 13:Slush [TAB for analysis id] 24718:Reads_QC__10-8-2024_Strain0016
